WEBVTT

00:02:59.516 --> 00:03:01.382
by creating alternative media.

00:03:01.829 --> 00:03:04.673
There are a variety of methods
that can be used to do this.

00:03:05.384 --> 00:03:08.176
My colleague and mentor, Gene Sharp,

00:03:08.200 --> 00:03:12.827
has identified 198 methods
of nonviolent action.

00:03:14.186 --> 00:03:15.951
And protest is only one.

00:03:16.376 --> 00:03:18.373
Let me give you a recent example.

00:03:18.885 --> 00:03:20.354
Until a few months ago,

00:03:20.378 --> 00:03:23.595
Guatemala was ruled
by corrupt former military officials

00:03:23.619 --> 00:03:25.430
with ties to organized crime.

00:03:26.071 --> 00:03:27.864
People were generally aware of this,

00:03:27.888 --> 00:03:31.238
but most of them felt powerless
to do anything about it --